<div id="leftCol">  
<h2>Accelerate with Red Hat Services</h2>
<p style="font-size:150%;">Address both the product and services needs of your clients while driving incremental revenue for your company.</p>
<p>The Partner Services Referral Program awards partners for referring qualified leads to Red Hat for direct services sale and delivery. Incentives are in the form of tiered, fixed fees for services engagements booked within 180 days of referral approval and delivered within twelve months of booking.</p>
<p>The process is simple. Simply submit leads via the services tab in Red Hat Deal Registration and earn incremental revenue on those leads that convert to wins.</p>
<h3>Benefits:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Creates incremental revenue opportunities for partners and fuels additional product sales.</li>
    <li>Learn and leverage Red Hat services with minimal initial investment.</li>
    <li>Easy to use referral registration system.</li>
</ul>
<h3>The Services Referral program is great for partners who are:</h3>
<ul>
    <li>Selling Red Hat products and looking to increase value-add for clients..</li>
    <li>Without a professional services core competency</li>
    <li>Looking to build a business case for services capabilities around Red Hat products.</li>
</ul>
